@toollean v0.1
@tool web_fetch
@desc Fetch and extract readable content from a URL (HTML to markdown/text)
@tags web,scraping,fetch
@in url:str HTTP or HTTPS URL to fetch
@in extractMode:str(markdown/text)? Extraction mode
@in maxChars:int? Maximum characters to return
@out content:str Extracted page content
@out title:str? Page title
@example Fetch a webpage
  > {"url": "https://example.com", "extractMode": "markdown"}
